title: Day 900
content:
# Day 900

10 things I want to do in the next 100 days

- Set a date for my wedding

- Build a SaaS app with a free and paid tier

- Get at least one customer

- Close (iykyk)

- Continue writing so I get to 1000 days of writing

- Be more purposeful in my writing (use this Medium as a way to hold myself accountable to the things I want to do in life, like build a SaaS app that gets at least one customer, 0 > 1, an infinity x if you think about it. You had nothing and now you have something. BOOM!

- Consistently workout with my Father 4x a week

- Figure out how to automate my work better

- Eat more meat, less bread

![BOOM. Lfg.](https://miro.medium.com/1*W-HvixMI5FBhymt8W17Aqg.png)

- Fast for at least 24 hours

9/7/24

Conor Jay Chepenik
